data.description: This property features a downstairs bedroom and a full sized downstairs bathroom. It also has a large upstairs living room.     Plenty of living space for large and/or multiple families.     This beautifully maintained home offers a perfect blend of comfort and potential, located in a serene and quiet neighborhood. With 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, this spacious abode is perfect for families of all sizes.    Pride of ownership that shines through. Meticulously cared for property is impeccably clean, making it move-in ready for its new owners.    The backyard is a blank canvas awaiting your creative touch. Whether you envision a lush garden, an outdoor entertainment oasis, or a playground for the kids, this space is ready for your imagination to bring it to life.    This property also features an upstairs den and a bedroom with a full sized bathroom downstairs.     Located in a quiet, friendly neighborhood, you'll enjoy the benefits of modern amenities, including a nearby neighborhood park where you can unwind and enjoy the outdoors with family and friends.    Another of the standout features of this property is the PAID-OFF SOLAR SYSTEM, offering energy efficiency and substantial savings on utility bills.    Don't miss this opportunity to make 604 Bailey Ln your new home – a well-cared-for gem in a tranquil setting, just waiting for you to add your personal touch.
